{"books":[{"id":"maoquanji28","name":"毛泽东全集第28卷","internal":false,"type":"pdf","official":false,"author":"张迪杰","files":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/maoquanji28.pdf"],"article":{"title":"给毛桂昌的信","alias":"","parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"给毛桂昌的信"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（1950年5月21日）桂昌先生："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"数次来信，均已收到，感谢你的好意。你家生活，应在土地改革中听候当地人民政府酌量分配土地，从努力生产中求得解决。此复，即祝康吉！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一九五○年五月二十一日"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"[1]毛桂昌（1894—1958），湖南省韶山市韶山乡韶源村人，后迁居湖南省沅江县，农民。毛泽东的远房叔父。大革命时期曾参加韶山农民运动。"}],"authors":["毛泽东"],"dates":[{"year":1950,"month":5,"day":21}],"is_range_date":false,"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":417,"page_end":417},"tags":[{"name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"type":"文稿类型","name":"书信"}]}]}